---
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Page
	title="Privacy Policy"
	description="Learn how The Thoughtful Pet collects, uses, and protects your personal information."
	image="/images/automatic-feeder.jpg"
	breadcrumbs={[
		{ label: 'Home', href: '/' },
		{ label: 'Privacy Policy', href: '/privacy-policy' },
	]}
	showNewsletter={false}
>
	<p>
		Last updated: June 23, 2026.
	</p>

	<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
	<p>
		When you subscribe to our newsletter or contact us, we may collect your email address and any information you voluntarily provide. We do not sell or rent your personal information.
	</p>

	<h2>Cookies and Analytics</h2>
	<p>
		We use cookies and similar technologies to understand how visitors use our site. We also use Google Analytics to analyze traffic and improve our content. You can disable cookies in your browser settings.
	</p>

	<h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
	<p>
		Some links on this site are affiliate links. Clicking these links may place a cookie on your device so the retailer can credit us for the referral. Please see our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for more details.
	</p>

	<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
	<p>
		We may use trusted third-party services for email subscriptions, analytics, and hosting. These services have their own privacy policies and only process data on our behalf.
	</p>

	<h2>Data Security</h2>
	<p>
		We take reasonable measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the internet is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
	</p>

	<h2>Your Rights</h2>
	<p>
		You may unsubscribe from our emails at any time by clicking the unsubscribe link at the bottom of any message. You may also contact us to request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data.
	</p>

	<h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
	<p>
		We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The latest version will always be posted on this page.
	</p>

	<h2>Contact Us</h2>
	<p>
		If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please <a href="/contact/">contact us</a>.
	</p>
</Page>
